## üéØ GOAL OF MVP:

> ‚ÄúA fully working e-commerce website where users can browse products, add to cart, purchase securely via Razorpay, and track their order ‚Äî with admin able to manage everything from backend.‚Äù

So the MVP must handle:
‚úÖ Full shopping journey
‚úÖ Payment
‚úÖ Admin management
‚úÖ Notifications for order updates

---

## üß© Essential Modules for MVP (Must-Have to Launch)

| #                                           | Module                                                                    | Why it‚Äôs essential |
| ------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------ |
| 1. Auth Module                          | Users need to register/login to place orders and manage accounts.         |                    |
| 2. User Module                          | Profile + address management for checkout and shipping.                   |                    |
| 3. Product Module                       | Core of e-commerce ‚Äî browse, view details, manage inventory.              |                    |
| 4. Cart Module                          | Users must add/remove/update products before checkout.                    |                    |
| 5. Order Module                         | Create and manage orders (pending, confirmed, delivered).                 |                    |
| 6. Payment Module                       | Razorpay integration for real transactions.                               |                    |
| 7. Invoice Module                       | Generate and send invoices for completed payments.                        |                    |
| 8. Dashboard & Analytics Module (Admin) | Admin view: total sales, products, orders, users ‚Äî critical for business. |                    |
| 9. Notification Module                  | Send order confirmation and status updates to users via email or SMS.     |                    |
| 10. Tracking Module                     | Allow customers to track their order/shipping status.                     |                    |

‚úÖ Total MVP Modules: 10
That‚Äôs a complete end-to-end flow (user ‚Üí cart ‚Üí payment ‚Üí invoice ‚Üí tracking).

