## ‚ö° MVP Flow (End-to-End)


Auth ‚Üí User ‚Üí Product ‚Üí Cart ‚Üí Order ‚Üí Payment ‚Üí Invoice ‚Üí Notification ‚Üí Tracking ‚Üí Dashboard(Admin)


That‚Äôs your minimum functional loop ‚Äî from browsing ‚Üí buying ‚Üí delivery ‚Üí admin control.

---

## üß≠ Suggested MVP Development Order (Step-by-Step)

| Phase       | Module                | Focus                                  |
| ----------- | --------------------- | -------------------------------------- |
| Phase 1 | Auth, User            | Setup secure user system               |
| Phase 2 | Product, Cart         | Core shopping logic                    |
| Phase 3 | Order, Payment        | Full checkout + Razorpay integration   |
| Phase 4 | Invoice, Notification | Automate receipts & updates            |
| Phase 5 | Tracking, Dashboard   | Add delivery tracking & admin insights |

